<title type="html"><![CDATA[Need help using CopyNES to combine .chr and.prg into .nes]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5298&amp;p=48153#p48153"><![CDATA[
Bumping this up because I figured out what I was doing wrong and it may help others avoid the same mistake.<br /><br />I was putting my .prg files and .chr files in their corresponding folders in the CopyNES directory.  In order to combine a .chr with a .prg file, they need to not only be named the same thing, but also located in the same folder.  If not, you end up getting a shit .nes file.<br /><br />Thanks for the help guys, I really appreciate it!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3334">mrmark0673</a> — Sun Jun 21, 2009 4:03 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
