<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5298&amp;p=47937#p47937"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Need help using CopyNES to combine .chr and.prg into .nes]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5298&amp;p=47937#p47937"><![CDATA[
UNROM is CHR RAM, so there is no CHR file to combine.  <br /><br />The other way is to start with a .nes file, and only keep the first 16 bytes.  Then paste in your PRG followed by your CHR.  Use an app like Nintendulator which has a iNES header editor.  There you can enter in the correct values for mapper and prg/chr sizes.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=228">bunnyboy</a> — Fri Jun 12, 2009 2:37 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
